{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Eekſch Iſraëta ne bija\nwairs Zeemi/ tee ne bija wairs/\nteekins es Debora zehlohs/ ka-\nmehr es zehlohs/ weena Mahte\neekſch Iſraëta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. (Iſraels) tſraudſtjahs jan-\nnus Deewus/ tad bija Kaṙra-\nWiḣri Wahrtis/ nei Preeſchtur-\nramas Bruunas nedś Schehps\ntappe eeraudſihts ſarp tſcheṭr-\nDefſmits tuhkfſoscheem eekſch I-\nfraëta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Manna Sirds irr ar teem\nteem Walditajeem eekſch Iſraëta/ kaṡ\nirr dahiwajchees ſarp teem Lau-\ndim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Teizeet to KUNGU juhs/\nkaṡ juhs uṡ baltahm Ebsetu-\nMahteem jahjt/ kaṡ juhs Tee-\nfâ febschat/ un kaṡ juhs pa Zettu\nstaigajat/ runnajt (no ta.)\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Kur to Strehtneeku Trohḳ-\nſnis bija/ ſarp tahm Weetahin/\nkur Uhdens fmelts tohp/ tur laid\nſluddina no tahs Taifnibas ta\nKUNGA/ no tahs Taifnibas pee\nwinna Zeemeem eekſch Iſraëta /\ntad nogabje uṡ Wahrtim ta\nKUNGA Laudis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Uṣmoḥsti/ uṣmoḥsti De-\nbora/ uṣmoḥsti/ uṣmoḥsti/ dsee-\ndajt Dſeefimu/ Zellees Barakṣ/\nun ſaguhſti tawus Gubſtitajus/\ntu Abinoama Dehis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Tad waldtja tee Atlikku-\nſchee/ tee Laudts pahr teem Aug-\nſteem/ tas KUNG S waldtja\nzaur maṅ pahr teem Warreneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. No Gewraima bija winnu\nSakne prett Amaleki/ un pehz\ntew Benjaminis ſarp taweem\nLaudim/ no Makira irr Wald-\nneeki nahkuschi/ un no Sebula-\nna/ kaṡ ar Spalwahn raksta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Ir Ihsachara Wirfneeki\nbija ar Debora/ un Ihsachars\nbija lihdska Baraks/ wiṣsch tap-\npe faweem Rahjuuekeem fuhtihts\nEeleija/ kad Rubbens fchkfhrabs/\nangſtas bija winna Sirds-Doh-\nmas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Kapehz palikki tu ſarp\nteem Laidareem? ka tu dsirdetuto\nSwilpeschanu pee teem Ganna-\nma-Pulkeem/ tu fchkhrees Ruh-\nbens / (turredams) angſtas\nSirds-Dohmas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Gileads palikfe winnpufs\nJardanas/ un Dans kapehz miht\npee leelahm Latwahm? Ahſers feh-\ndeja Juhrmallā/ un palikfe eekſch\nfawahm plihfuſchahm Weetahm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Sebulans irr tee Laudis/\nkaṡ fanehmahs Drohfchibā lihds\npatt Nahwei/Nawtalus arridsan\nTihruma Augſtuuā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Tee Kehnini nahze/tee kak-\nroja/ tad karroja tee Kehnini no\nKanaāna eekſch Taānata pee ta\nUhdens Megiddus/tee ne dabbuja\nne kahdu Naudas Pelzu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. No Debbes tappe prett\nteem karrohts / tahs Swaigſnes\nno fawahm angſtam Weetahm\nkarroja prett Siffern.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Ta Kisona Uppe nowchle\nwinnaus/ ta Uppe Redunim/ ta\nUppe Kisons / tu efi manna\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
